00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:56,920
and you’d get paid,

240
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,000
yet you didn’t listen.

241
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,760
Splashing hot water over you is nothing.

242
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:01,440
What if they beat you?

243
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:03,280
I had to try it.

244
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:05,680
Or how would I know if the new lines work?

245
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,000
Bring me liquor.

246
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:17,640
Leader,

247
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:18,600
here it is.

248
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:25,440
Mr. Cheng,

249
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:26,440
this way, please.

250
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,080
It’s still here.

251
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,520
What to do?

252
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,480
Mr. Shang,

253
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,600
you have a visitor.

254
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:41,880
Mr. Shang,

255
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:43,880
this is Mr. Cheng, Cheng Fengtai.

256
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:47,520
Mr. Shang,

257
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:48,960
you must be startled.

258
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:50,880
Thanks for your help.

259
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,680
You were hurt?

260
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:56,160
I’m really sorry.

261
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:58,840
You saw it?

262
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:01,520
You seemed calm on the stage.

263
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:04,720
Calm?

264
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,400
I’m trained

265
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:07,600
to always stay calm.

266
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:09,600
Leader. Where did the ring hit?

267
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,360
Let me see.

268
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,520
You're bruised!

269
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:13,600
Don’t panic.

270
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,640
I’m fine.

271
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:17,040
I apologize.

272
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:20,560
Those hooligans didn’t hurt you,

273
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:22,480
but we did.

274
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,800
Mi...Miss,

275
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:25,960
I'm sorry.

276
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,480
I didn’t mean to throw it at you.

277
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,840
No need to apologize.

278
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:33,840
I appreciate your gift.

279
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,040
Thank you.

280
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:37,080
Oh, silly.

281
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:39,720
That’s not a pretty girl.

282
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:42,520
Call him Mister.

283
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:44,840
She wasn’t wrong.

284
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:46,280
I haven’t removed my makeup.

285
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,380
My character is a girl.

286
00:09:47,380 --> 00:09:47,560
(La Yuehong)
My character is a girl.

287
00:09:47,560 --> 00:09:48,540
(La Yuehong)

288
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,760
Mr. Shang,

289
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:53,600
let me take you back after you get changed.

290
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,800
It’s safer that way.

291
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,080
Thank you,

292
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,080
but no need.

293
00:09:58,400 --> 00:09:59,800
I still have to

294
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,200
pack up to move.

295
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,800
It takes time.

296
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,200
Move?

297
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:05,960
You aren’t going to perform?

298
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,720
I will

299
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,200
but not in here.

300
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:10,640
Why, Mr. Shang?

301
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,040
What’s going on?

302
00:10:12,040 --> 00:10:12,960
Why are you leaving?

303
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,520
Did I do anything wrong?

304
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:15,960
You've been attentive enough.

305
00:10:16,280 --> 00:10:17,040
At least,

306
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:19,160
those men didn’t get on the stage.

307
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:20,960
You aren’t at fault.

308
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,760
It’s my decision to leave.

309
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:24,080
I feel guilty.

310
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:26,680
Fine.

311
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:28,600
Those goons

312
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:29,640
gave you a hard time.

313
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:30,680
It's my fault.

314
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:31,440
Look,

315
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:33,840
I’ll pay you fees for the whole month

316
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:34,600
as compensation

317
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:36,760
but please do me a favor.

318
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,200
I have no substitutes for this month.

319
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:41,040
Please perform one last time

320
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:42,240
before you leave.

321
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,200
Is that OK?

322
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:45,520
I’m obligated to do that

323
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,520
and I won’t take extra money from you.

324
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:48,960
But I have one condition.

325
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,360
What is it?

326
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:52,480
Today’s Drunken Beauty is ruined.

327
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:55,680
My last performance will still be this piece

328
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,520
Deal.

329
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,320
As long as you can go on the stage,

330
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:00,960
you can sing whatever you please.

331
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:07,960
I’m sorry

332
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,600
that you have to see this.

333
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,560
Since you're busy,

334
00:11:13,040 --> 00:11:15,480
I’ll take my leave then.

335
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,760
It’s a mess here.

336
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,040
I won’t make you stay.

337
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:21,040
Thanks again.

338
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,040
Xiao Lai.

339
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:24,840
Pick out

340
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,240
my best coat

341
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,360
for Mr. Cheng to wear.

342
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,160
No need.

343
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:31,240
Just take it.

344
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:32,360
It’s cold outside.

345
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,560
Thank you, Mr. Shang.

346
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,520
Mr. Cheng.

347
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:41,640
Mr. Cheng,

348
00:11:41,640 --> 00:11:43,680
don’t thank me again.

349
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:46,840
You agreed to repair my costume

350
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,360
and injured yourself because of me.

351
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,680
I owe you too much.

352
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,880
You knew me before?

353
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:58,840
You handled all my embroidered costumes.

354
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:01,560
I’m familiar with the freight agency.

355
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:03,280
How could I not know the owner?

356
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,640
Today’s performance failed.

357
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:07,960
You're welcome to watch it again.

358
00:12:08,160 --> 00:12:08,920
Sure.

359
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,440
I’ll come

360
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:12,240
whenever I have time.

361
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,200
My pleasure.

362
00:12:17,640 --> 00:12:18,440
Do take care.

363
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:19,640
Mr. Shang,

364
00:12:20,280 --> 00:12:21,080
good day.

365
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:50,140
(Shang Xirui)

366
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,400
Are you mad at me?

367
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:02,600
You played hero tonight.

368
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:04,640
Aren’t you tired?

369
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:12,600
A hero is still no match for you.

370
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:15,840
Can’t laugh. Can’t laugh.

371
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,760
Knock it off.

372
00:13:19,560 --> 00:13:21,040
We've been married for so long

373
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:24,000
yet I didn’t know you could fight.

374
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,560
Don’t you know who Shang Xirui is?

375
00:13:27,920 --> 00:13:29,480
A superstar.

376
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:32,800
He's seen tons of fans fighting for him.

377
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:36,840
Were you not so well-respected,

378
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:40,200
he wouldn’t glance at you even if you died.

379
00:13:42,520 --> 00:13:44,440
He got booed.

380
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:45,920
Why did you care so much?

381
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:48,080
Just mind your own business.

382
00:13:51,760 --> 00:13:54,000
It’s nothing strange

383
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,680
that men engage in fights.

384
00:13:56,680 --> 00:13:58,840
Don’t be so furious.

385
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:00,960
I know

386
00:14:01,520 --> 00:14:02,960
I have no place to lecture you.

387
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:08,200
I came here from the other side of the country

388
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:10,560
to marry you without asking you for a penny.

389
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,360
You had no choice

390
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:13,640
but to take me in.

391
00:14:16,160 --> 00:14:18,200
An ignorant country girl like me

392
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,720
is no match

393
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:23,120
for the rich and handsome Mr. Cheng.

394
00:14:25,520 --> 00:14:27,760
Why you bring that up whenever you're mad?

395
00:14:29,160 --> 00:14:30,520
Marrying you

396
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:33,840
is the smartest thing I’ve ever done.

397
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:37,160
I know how good you are.

398
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:44,560
Forget about tonight’s incident.

399
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:46,920
I was reckless.

400
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:48,280
I’m sorry.

401
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:50,680
But don't listen to them.

402
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:52,480
It wasn’t a real fight.

403
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,360
Look,

404
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:01,720
Chacha’er is a big girl now.

405
00:15:03,160 --> 00:15:05,560
Don’t bring her with you to run around.

406
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:10,120
Yes, ma’am.

407
00:15:13,640 --> 00:15:14,680
Does it still hurt?

408
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:16,360
Yes.

409
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:20,480
A kiss will remove the pain.

410
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,760
You deserve it.

411
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:24,920
Ouch!

412
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:27,720
You bring this to yourself.

413
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:44,400
Earlier in Huibin Theater,

414
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:47,720
manager did nothing when the thugs made a scene.

415
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:50,200
That was to embarrass our leader.

416
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:52,360
How rude!

417
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:56,440
You were at fault, too.

418
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,280
You were impulsive

419
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:00,400
by telling him to quit.

420
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:03,800
I didn’t sing by the book

421
00:16:05,160 --> 00:16:07,360
so the audience lashed out before I finished.

422
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:10,280
I know the theater lost money

423
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:11,960
because of me.

424
00:16:12,520 --> 00:16:13,320
I’m not stupid.

425
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:14,720
Tonight,

426
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:16,880
they caught a chance to get back at me

427
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:19,520
by letting those men stirring up trouble.

428
00:16:19,760 --> 00:16:20,960
I don’t want to stay there anymore.

429
00:16:22,880 --> 00:16:25,120
We can quit after we find the next hirer.

430
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:27,000
Our troupe has to support dozens of people.

431
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,120
If we can’t get paid,

432
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:29,440
how will we live?

433
00:16:29,800 --> 00:16:32,440
Huibin isn't the only theater in town.

434
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,240
We can perform in another theater.

435
00:16:34,880 --> 00:16:36,960
A few already contacted me a while ago.

436
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:38,280
Just pick one from them.

437
00:16:39,680 --> 00:16:40,320
Uh...

438
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:42,360
I asked Xiao Lai to prepare a gift.

439
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:45,240
Bring it to Jiang Rongshou yourself later.

440
00:16:45,880 --> 00:16:47,320
You didn’t show up on his birthday.

441
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:49,080
I heard

442
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:51,080
he was furious.

443
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,080
I won’t go.

444
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:54,480
You have to.

445
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:56,440
The Jiangs are deeply rooted.

446
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:57,760
You should know

447
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,560
newcomers shouldn’t challenge the locals.

448
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:03,680
You're afraid of Jiang Rongshou

449
00:17:04,520 --> 00:17:06,079
but not me?

450
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:12,160
I don’t get what you're worried about.

451
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:14,760
I’m still popular.

452
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:17,680
As long as people still love my performance,

453
00:17:18,119 --> 00:17:19,319
they’re willing to pay for it,

454
00:17:19,640 --> 00:17:21,000
and fans still support me

455
00:17:21,280 --> 00:17:22,599
why waste time on those formalities?

456
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:26,520
If I go, I’ll have to call Jiang Rongshou uncle.

457
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:27,880
I don’t want to!

458
00:17:28,840 --> 00:17:29,640
Eat.

459
00:17:31,080 --> 00:17:32,640
Let's eat. Dig in.

460
00:17:43,040 --> 00:17:44,560
Mr. Jiang. Mr. Jiang.

461
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:47,040
Mr. Jiang.

462
00:17:48,120 --> 00:17:49,200
Here. Here. Here.

463
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:49,960
Come here.

464
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:51,000
Come.

465
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:56,880
I was looking for you.

466
00:17:58,320 --> 00:18:00,720
How did it go last night?

467
00:18:00,800 --> 00:18:01,640
Mr. Jiang.

468
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:03,880
My brother and the others were arrested.

469
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:04,840
What?

470
00:18:05,840 --> 00:18:07,320
Why did the cops arrest him?

471
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:09,200
We were in bad luck.

472
00:18:09,520 --> 00:18:10,640
That performer was fine

473
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:12,360
but we hit Commander Cao's brother-in-law.

474
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:14,880
Only I got out.

475
00:18:15,360 --> 00:18:17,880
His brother-in-law told the commissioner

476
00:18:18,520 --> 00:18:20,920
not to release them until they confess.

477
00:18:29,240 --> 00:18:31,800
We had a deal.

478
00:18:32,520 --> 00:18:34,360
You’d take responsibility.

479
00:18:35,080 --> 00:18:36,920
Leave me out of it.

480
00:18:37,600 --> 00:18:38,280
But...

481
00:18:42,120 --> 00:18:43,240
Listen,

482
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:46,040
we never met today.

483
00:18:48,640 --> 00:18:50,240
I don’t know you.

484
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:55,440
Wait, Mr. Jiang.

485
00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:56,640
You can’t do this.

486
00:18:58,120 --> 00:18:59,000
Mr. Jiang.

487
00:18:59,280 --> 00:19:00,720
Don’t go.

488
00:19:17,720 --> 00:19:18,880
Alright, Mr. Jiang,

489
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:19,560
that's all for today.

490
00:19:19,560 --> 00:19:20,600
We’re leaving.

491
00:19:20,600 --> 00:19:21,360
Take care.

492
00:19:21,360 --> 00:19:21,920
Sure.

493
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:34,400
Father.

494
00:19:35,600 --> 00:19:36,640
Drinking tea?

495
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:39,080
Come here.

496
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:44,880
Kneel.

497
00:19:47,720 --> 00:19:49,600
Last night, a few goons

498
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:51,520
ruined Shang Xirui's performance.

499
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:53,880
Were you behind that?

500
00:19:54,600 --> 00:19:55,600
No.

501
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:56,520
I...

502
00:19:56,520 --> 00:19:57,640
Don’t deny it.

503
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,120
Right after they were arrested,

504
00:20:00,120 --> 00:20:02,400
they gave the police your name.

505
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,240
Yes, I did it.

506
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:11,520
How dare Shang Xirui

507
00:20:11,520 --> 00:20:14,320
ride roughshod over us on our territory!

508
00:20:18,600 --> 00:20:20,120
Listen to yourself.

509
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:22,640
You’re a fool.

510
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:28,640
Shang Xirui is a rising star in the city.

511
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:31,120
If everyone knows

512
00:20:32,040 --> 00:20:33,520
you set him up,

513
00:20:34,800 --> 00:20:37,600
they’ll all take his side.

514
00:20:38,520 --> 00:20:40,200
How will that benefit you?

515
00:20:53,300 --> 00:20:53,860
Father.

516
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:56,120
We’ll just let him be?

517
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,840
There’s still plenty of time.

518
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:02,840
Be patient.

519
00:21:05,120 --> 00:21:07,400
You should hit where it hurts the most.

520
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:13,640
Your trick didn’t damage him at all

521
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:15,000
but only backfired.

522
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:17,640
Use your brain.

523
00:21:29,900 --> 00:21:37,580
♫ Clear clouds and gentle breezes ♫

524
00:21:39,060 --> 00:21:40,500
♫ Flowers all blossom ♫

525
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:42,100
Who is this?

526
00:21:42,100 --> 00:21:42,200
♫ What a wonderful spring ♫
Who is this?

527
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:43,320
♫ What a wonderful spring ♫

528
00:21:43,320 --> 00:21:45,200
He seems popular.
♫ What a wonderful spring ♫

529
