808
00:33:25,520 --> 00:33:26,800
Look ahead.

809
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:28,680
Move.

810
00:33:28,880 --> 00:33:30,000
Go up.

811
00:33:30,320 --> 00:33:31,160
Higher.

812
00:33:31,320 --> 00:33:32,200
Lift your arms.

813
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:33,720
Lower your shoulders.

814
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:34,660
Good.

815
00:33:34,860 --> 00:33:36,280
What are you doing?

816
00:33:36,280 --> 00:33:37,160
Lower your shoulders.

817
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:39,400
Hold it.

818
00:33:47,640 --> 00:33:48,360
You’re practicing hard.

819
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:49,760
Hello, Mr. Niu.

820
00:33:50,080 --> 00:33:50,960
Mr. Shang,

821
00:33:50,960 --> 00:33:51,760
you busy?

822
00:33:51,760 --> 00:33:52,280
Not too busy.

823
00:33:52,280 --> 00:33:53,600
Just watching the kids practicing.

824
00:33:53,600 --> 00:33:54,000
Xiao Lai.

825
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:54,880
Serve tea.

826
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:56,000
Have a seat.

827
00:33:56,680 --> 00:33:58,280
I’ll bring you some tea.

828
00:33:58,280 --> 00:33:59,400
Thank you.

829
00:33:59,680 --> 00:34:00,520
You’re welcome.

830
00:34:01,560 --> 00:34:02,720
What's up?

831
00:34:02,720 --> 00:34:04,200
You have no work to do?

832
00:34:04,560 --> 00:34:06,640
Minister Jin proposed the donation.

833
00:34:07,040 --> 00:34:09,159
He asked us to perform for charity.

834
00:34:09,560 --> 00:34:10,360
This is the list of operas.

835
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:11,679
Choose one you like.

836
00:34:12,520 --> 00:34:13,840
When I saw the banner

837
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:15,760
in the street, I was thinking

838
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:17,080
about joining the charity performance

839
00:34:17,320 --> 00:34:18,560
if there was one.

840
00:34:20,480 --> 00:34:22,639
But this time is different.

841
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:24,400
We have to perform in plain clothes.

842
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:25,280
No costumes

843
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:27,000
or huqin.

844
00:34:27,800 --> 00:34:28,840
But don't worry,

845
00:34:28,840 --> 00:34:29,639
I have

846
00:34:29,639 --> 00:34:31,440
one of the best musicians for you.

847
00:34:32,679 --> 00:34:34,400
So we’ll perform for free,

848
00:34:34,679 --> 00:34:35,920
meals not included?

849
00:34:38,239 --> 00:34:39,760
Of course not.

850
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:41,239
Don’t worry.

851
00:34:41,239 --> 00:34:42,560
You won't be starved.

852
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:46,880
Will Mr. Ning, Ning Jiulang be there?

853
00:34:47,159 --> 00:34:47,840
No.

854
00:34:48,199 --> 00:34:50,159
He’s chanting sutras all day

855
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:51,280
and seldom leaves the house.

856
00:34:51,600 --> 00:34:53,440
Duke Qi donated money for him.

857
00:34:54,080 --> 00:34:55,719
What about Mr. Hou, Hou Yukui?

858
00:34:56,440 --> 00:34:57,240
He won’t come either.

859
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:04,240
So just me alone?

860
00:35:04,560 --> 00:35:05,540
It sucks.

861
00:35:05,540 --> 00:35:05,920
(Second Time in the Palace)
It sucks.

862
00:35:05,920 --> 00:35:07,200
(Second Time in the Palace)

863
00:35:07,200 --> 00:35:07,620
This is it.
(Second Time in the Palace)

864
00:35:07,620 --> 00:35:08,080
This is it.

865
00:35:10,160 --> 00:35:11,240
Wait, Mr. Shang.

866
00:35:11,240 --> 00:35:12,440
Choose another one.

867
00:35:12,680 --> 00:35:14,400
Second Time in the Palace is too flat.

868
00:35:14,400 --> 00:35:15,440
Not enough excitement.

869
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:17,280
I’ll make it exciting.

870
00:35:20,080 --> 00:35:20,800
Alright then.

871
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:22,360
No wonder you're so popular.

872
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:24,040
I’m leaving.

873
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,360
Goodbye, Mr. Niu.

874
00:35:26,080 --> 00:35:26,840
Take care.

875
00:35:26,840 --> 00:35:27,560
See you. Goodbye.

876
00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:29,240
Take care.

877
00:35:30,080 --> 00:35:31,060
-Continue.
-Keep practicing.

878
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:31,240
(Peking Opera Performance Fund-raising Event)
-Continue.
-Keep practicing.

879
00:35:31,240 --> 00:35:40,500
(Peking Opera Performance Fund-raising Event)

880
00:35:41,520 --> 00:35:43,120
-Long time no see.
-It’s been a while.

881
00:35:50,640 --> 00:35:53,440
Cripple Jin is brazen.

882
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:56,200
He simply arranges a small show

883
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,920
to get money out of our pockets.

884
00:35:59,040 --> 00:36:00,840
What is this?

885
00:36:03,400 --> 00:36:05,320
You don’t understand.

886
00:36:07,200 --> 00:36:08,280
Money we donate

887
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:10,720
has two uses.

888
00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:12,320
First,

889
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:14,120
he can keep it to himself.

890
00:36:15,640 --> 00:36:16,440
Second,

891
00:36:18,160 --> 00:36:20,320
he can give it to Commander Cao

892
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:23,320
in the name of rewarding the army

893
00:36:23,680 --> 00:36:25,920
to win political merits.

894
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:30,400
How calculative!

895
00:36:32,240 --> 00:36:33,200
I thought

896
00:36:33,200 --> 00:36:35,200
Commander Cao would dismiss him.

897
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:37,680
But once he takes the money,

898
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:40,760
he can’t give him a hard time.

899
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:43,640
Not exactly.

900
00:36:44,160 --> 00:36:45,920
One nation can't have two kings.

901
00:36:47,040 --> 00:36:49,560
Either Cripple Jin will have to leave

902
00:36:50,200 --> 00:36:52,440
or Commander Cao will.

903
00:36:54,160 --> 00:36:55,320
Forget about that.

904
00:36:55,600 --> 00:36:56,920
It’s none of our business.

905
00:36:57,320 --> 00:36:58,880
We’re here today

906
00:36:59,240 --> 00:37:00,640
to enjoy Xirui’s opera.

907
00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:02,920
He’ll be here, too?

908
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:04,200
Of course.

909
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:05,440
He’s famous.

910
00:37:06,320 --> 00:37:08,280
How could he be left out?

911
00:37:11,040 --> 00:37:11,920
Fine.

912
00:37:13,120 --> 00:37:15,080
I’ll try to enjoy the show.

913
00:37:17,920 --> 00:37:19,880
If I hang out more with you,

914
00:37:20,320 --> 00:37:22,400
I’ll be an opera expert.

915
00:37:23,640 --> 00:37:25,400
Just sit and listen.

916
00:37:25,600 --> 00:37:27,560
Don’t hum at home,

917
00:37:29,040 --> 00:37:30,920
or my two sisters will kill me.

918
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:31,720
I mean it.

919
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:33,200
How’s the preparation going?

920
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:35,640
Rest assured, Mr. Jin.

921
00:37:35,640 --> 00:37:38,760
My father has made it flawlessly.

922
00:37:39,320 --> 00:37:40,480
That's good.

923
00:37:40,840 --> 00:37:42,440
Don't leave, Mr. Zhao.

924
00:37:43,000 --> 00:37:43,720
Mr. Zhao,

925
00:37:44,160 --> 00:37:45,640
the show hasn’t started.

926
00:37:45,640 --> 00:37:47,120
If you leave, how will Mr. Shang sing?

927
00:37:47,120 --> 00:37:48,360
He can do whatever he likes.

928
00:37:48,440 --> 00:37:49,920
I’m unable to serve him.

929
00:37:50,640 --> 00:37:51,800
Mr. Zhao...

930
00:37:52,080 --> 00:37:53,800
What’s happening?

931
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:00,680
Mr. Zhao. Mr. Zhao.

932
00:38:00,800 --> 00:38:01,960
We're about to begin.

933
00:38:01,960 --> 00:38:03,480
Mr. Shang can’t sing without you.

934
00:38:03,480 --> 00:38:04,700
Don’t go, Mr. Zhao.

935
00:38:04,700 --> 00:38:05,660
Mr. Zhao. Come back.

936
00:38:05,680 --> 00:38:06,120
Mr. Zhao,

937
00:38:06,120 --> 00:38:07,400
listen to me, listen.

938
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:08,680
We need you, Mr. Zhao.

939
00:38:19,080 --> 00:38:20,040
Niu Baiwen.

940
00:38:20,040 --> 00:38:20,800
Come here.

941
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:25,920
Minister Jin.

942
00:38:27,440 --> 00:38:28,400
What's wrong?

943
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:29,760
Nothing.

944
00:38:33,400 --> 00:38:34,880
Tell Shang Xirui,

945
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:36,480
most people are here today

946
00:38:36,520 --> 00:38:37,800
to watch

947
00:38:37,800 --> 00:38:39,520
his performance.

948
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:42,440
If anything goes south,

949
00:38:43,000 --> 00:38:45,280
he’ll have to answer to my gun.

950
00:38:46,280 --> 00:38:47,160
Yes.

951
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:48,440
I’ll make the arrangement.

952
00:38:57,780 --> 00:38:58,380
Father.

953
00:39:01,160 --> 00:39:02,440
Come here.

954
00:39:03,640 --> 00:39:06,160
I’m sorry, so sorry.

955
00:39:10,360 --> 00:39:12,240
Our musician left.

956
00:39:14,160 --> 00:39:16,160
Shang Xirui drove him out.

957
00:39:18,680 --> 00:39:20,440
He does love drinking.

958
00:39:21,240 --> 00:39:22,000
You know that, right?

959
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:24,000
But Shang Xirui said he’d ruin the show.

960
00:39:25,240 --> 00:39:26,240
He’s well-known

961
00:39:26,240 --> 00:39:27,240
in the opera circle.

962
00:39:27,240 --> 00:39:28,520
So what if he drinks?

963
00:39:29,060 --> 00:39:29,740
Well,

964
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:32,040
he left in rage.

965
00:39:35,920 --> 00:39:37,440
Don’t you want to destroy Shang Xirui?

966
00:39:39,200 --> 00:39:41,040
This is your chance.

967
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:50,680
Your life is on the line.

968
00:39:50,680 --> 00:39:52,440
Aren’t you worried?

969
00:39:53,720 --> 00:39:55,720
He said to shoot me.

970
00:39:55,800 --> 00:39:57,200
Why are you panicking?

971
00:39:57,520 --> 00:39:58,920
Stop joking around!

972
00:39:58,920 --> 00:40:00,720
If something happens to you here,

973
00:40:00,720 --> 00:40:01,280
I...

974
00:40:02,960 --> 00:40:04,720
Don’t frown.

975
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:05,560
Relax.

976
00:40:05,560 --> 00:40:07,760
I’ll take care of it once my thing arrives.

977
00:40:08,080 --> 00:40:09,840
Your thing... Really?

978
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:11,960
Here it is.

979
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:12,680
Hi, Xiao Lai.

980
00:40:12,760 --> 00:40:13,360
Hi.

981
00:40:14,240 --> 00:40:15,120
Coming.

982
00:40:15,120 --> 00:40:15,800
What is this?

983
00:40:17,920 --> 00:40:19,720
You're waiting for this elbow?

984
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:21,320
Leader always says

985
00:40:21,320 --> 00:40:22,880
to sing with an empty stomach.

986
00:40:22,880 --> 00:40:24,560
Too much food will affect the breathing

987
00:40:24,720 --> 00:40:26,440
and the performer will throw up on the stage.

988
00:40:26,440 --> 00:40:27,880
But when it comes to himself,

989
00:40:27,880 --> 00:40:29,320
he doesn’t care.

990
00:40:29,920 --> 00:40:30,720
Miss Xiao Lai,

991
00:40:30,720 --> 00:40:32,000
that’s not fair.

992
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:32,880
All performers

993
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:34,480
have their own quirks before acting.

994
00:40:34,480 --> 00:40:35,240
You know,

995
00:40:35,240 --> 00:40:36,320
Mr. Hou, Hou Yukui,

996
00:40:36,320 --> 00:40:38,400
has to smoke before going on the stage.

997
00:40:38,480 --> 00:40:39,360
Ning Jiulang,

998
00:40:39,360 --> 00:40:40,560
following the rule in the palace,

999
00:40:40,880 --> 00:40:43,480
always has lotus seeds soup with white fungus.

1000
00:40:44,040 --> 00:40:45,560
Yuan Xiaodi is funnier.

1001
00:40:45,560 --> 00:40:46,880
He used to be a scholar

1002
00:40:46,880 --> 00:40:47,880
and is still a bookworm.

1003
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:48,880
Before he performs,

1004
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:50,720
he has to read Tao Te Ching.

1005
00:40:52,760 --> 00:40:54,920
Mr. Shang is more down to earth.

1006
00:40:55,440 --> 00:40:56,240
I admire you.

1007
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:02,360
Fantastic!

1008
00:41:04,880 --> 00:41:05,800
You got an idea?

1009
00:41:07,160 --> 00:41:07,880
Hold on.

1010
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:11,880
It’ll come soon.

1011
00:41:14,560 --> 00:41:15,520
Mr. Shang,

1012
00:41:17,080 --> 00:41:18,440
my father wants to see you.

1013
00:41:21,000 --> 00:41:23,080
You want me to apologize to you

1014
00:41:23,080 --> 00:41:24,440
in public

1015
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:26,560
and swear to be obedient in the future?

1016
00:41:28,680 --> 00:41:30,200
Isn’t that what you should do?

1017
00:41:31,200 --> 00:41:32,480
I’m sort of your uncle.

1018
00:41:33,640 --> 00:41:36,000
Of course I’ll help you.

1019
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:38,800
How do you plan to help me?

1020
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:41,200
Do you have a musician for me?

1021
00:41:45,120 --> 00:41:45,760
Outsiders

1022
00:41:45,760 --> 00:41:48,840
only know I’m a good performer.

1023
00:41:50,560 --> 00:41:52,280
What they don’t know is

1024
00:41:52,560 --> 00:41:55,360
I can also play the instrument.

1025
00:41:56,080 --> 00:41:57,320
I appreciate your offer.

1026
00:41:58,000 --> 00:41:59,000
Thank you

1027
00:41:59,000 --> 00:42:00,360
for trying to help me out.

1028
00:42:01,080 --> 00:42:03,000
But I caused the trouble

1029
00:42:03,480 --> 00:42:05,040
and I can’t bother you with it.

1030
00:42:05,920 --> 00:42:07,040
Kid,

1031
00:42:07,120 --> 00:42:09,200
you're young and may not know

1032
00:42:10,720 --> 00:42:12,280
that countless people

1033
00:42:12,680 --> 00:42:14,320
have died in Minister Jin’s hands.

1034
00:42:15,720 --> 00:42:17,560
He’s capable of anything.

1035
00:42:17,640 --> 00:42:19,840
So are you.

1036
00:42:21,800 --> 00:42:23,080
What’s that supposed to mean?

1037
00:42:23,400 --> 00:42:25,320
I simply missed your birthday banquet.

1038
00:42:25,520 --> 00:42:27,520
Yet you ordered them to scald me.

1039
00:42:28,080 --> 00:42:29,840
We don’t like each other.

1040
00:42:29,840 --> 00:42:31,520
Don’t pretend to be nice.

1041
00:42:34,880 --> 00:42:36,120
Fine.

1042
00:42:37,720 --> 00:42:39,600
Since you're so ungrateful,

1043
00:42:39,920 --> 00:42:41,840
I won’t waste my kindness on you.

1044
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:44,080
Shang Fengtai,

1045
00:42:46,720 --> 00:42:47,680
take care.

1046
00:42:58,360 --> 00:42:59,440
Mr. Cheng.

1047
00:42:59,440 --> 00:43:00,400
What a coincidence!

1048
00:43:00,400 --> 00:43:02,280
I meant to enjoy your opera,

1049
00:43:02,440 --> 00:43:04,320
but now, I guess I can’t.

1050
00:43:04,480 --> 00:43:05,600
Come with me.

1051
00:43:06,680 --> 00:43:08,040
Where are you taking me?

1052
00:43:08,960 --> 00:43:10,480
Don’t mess with Cripple Jin.

1053
00:43:10,800 --> 00:43:12,320
I already did.

1054
00:43:13,680 --> 00:43:14,480
Don’t worry.

1055
00:43:14,600 --> 00:43:16,160
You can stay at my agency.

1056
00:43:16,280 --> 00:43:17,680
He dares not to touch you.

1057
00:43:17,800 --> 00:43:20,040
You're used to playing hero to save beauties.

1058
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:21,840
You're a hero

1059
00:43:22,280 --> 00:43:23,720
but I’m not a beauty.

1060
00:43:24,000 --> 00:43:25,320
I’m also a hero.

1061
00:43:26,480 --> 00:43:27,560
Go back to enjoy the show.

1062
00:43:27,840 --> 00:43:29,360
You won’t be disappointed.
